result.title: why is codeforces c++14 compiler giving wrong answer ?
result.content: In hello 2018 round I wrote my submission to problem-C Party Lemonade, it ran well on geeksforgeeks c++14 compiler giving correct ans for test case 4 but the same code with same input gave wrong ans on codeforces c++14 compiler. why is it so.. mysubmission url:-http://codeforces.com/submissions/tibialAcorn98 submission no -34026659
